  <brief_title>An Open Label Extension Study of STX209 in Subjects With Fragile X Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label Extension Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of STX209 in Subjects With Fragile X Syndrome</official_title>
